{"id": 1309, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年，你都是怎么“凑合”过来的？", "description": "因为没达到理想的生活质量，今年你都做了哪些“凑合过吧”的妥协？（题图来自：Kelly Beeman）", "record_count": 2770, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016110416372230NQwTlL56Wu2HK4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-10T03:00:56Z", "options": [{"id": 132352, "content": "想把不到40平的出租屋弄的逼格高点，看了一圈想买的，最后想到每个月要还的贷款，要交的房屋，就凑合了\n趁着双十一买个锅，然后想到要早起好久做饭，就凑合了\n看着自己那点工资，还完钱想吃点好的，然后算了算每天只能允许自己花40块钱，就凑合了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476820}, {"id": 132354, "content": "过完今天，就得吃土。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732679}, {"id": 132355, "content": "想努力追求爱情，但还是自己受伤，就这么纠结着又过了一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742811}, {"id": 130308, "content": "很多次没时间好好吃饭，都是在便利店凑合", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 132284, "content": "什么都凑合！", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826116}, {"id": 132285, "content": "天天算着信用卡账单，想买的东西基本没买，只想赶快把信用卡还完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785945}, {"id": 132305, "content": "结婚的躁动", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 132325, "content": "总是抉择，抉择之后又开始忐忑。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167451}, {"id": 132353, "content": "本来想好好的练书法却一直没好好练，这个懒癌啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819357}, {"id": 134145, "content": "最近都不敢晒自己的照片了 也不敢见朋友了 你说怎么过来的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817785}, {"id": 135169, "content": "买完衣服后 很久没有吃零食 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839284}, {"id": 134146, "content": "最近都不敢晒自己的照片了 \n也不敢见家人朋友了 \n体重哗啦啦的往下降\n现在这个点儿眼睛还瞪着\n你说呢？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817785}, {"id": 137474, "content": "写好的离职报告放在抽屉很久了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689742}, {"id": 132356, "content": "买了喜欢的衣服，鞋，包，键盘，电脑等等，然后每天吃土", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433845}, {"id": 132868, "content": "在今年七月的海滩，我遇到一个姑娘，后来我来到上海，却和她分别了。我觉得这对我来说是生命中的一次转机，意味着完全不同的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690475}, {"id": 132357, "content": "过得像电视剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827875}, {"id": 130309, "content": "工作没有很喜欢，想想还是等耗到拿年终奖再说吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 335, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 132358, "content": "体重永远永远永远降不下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782858}, {"id": 132870, "content": "换房子住的时候看上一个140m的大三居，但房东价格比我预算多两千，于是去找了一个100m出头的大两居……结果今年太太怀孕，明年又还是得换。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525787}, {"id": 130310, "content": "想和对象分手却开不了口，没想到一拖就又是一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 132359, "content": "凑合苦闷的心情，“都苦闷这么久了，继续？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787250}, {"id": 130311, "content": "虽然给自己定了读书计划，但我把时装杂志也算进去凑数了......", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 132361, "content": "看看购物车，又看看男朋友的银行卡，决定不凑合的过双十一。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209120}, {"id": 130313, "content": "双十一内心躁动，但查看银行卡余额后觉得很多东西也还能凑合用", "image": null, "praise_count": 522, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 132362, "content": "想着减肥成功就买新衣服，总不成功，总没衣服，总没动力减肥，恶性循环……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673813}, {"id": 132874, "content": "比如学习吧，凑合了很多年，人生也就跟着凑合了许多年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830096}, {"id": 132363, "content": "年初打算考研，到现在也没有真正投入过，凑合到现在，不想再继续下去，成长从改变开始，加油", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828117}, {"id": 137739, "content": "觉着自己不至于太惨，先凑合", "image": "img/option/option/20161129144543bSJrws8hQRmGWB67.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850022}, {"id": 132364, "content": "想卸载好奇心日报，结果凑合着又看了一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 134156, "content": "三套衣服过完冬天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834442}, {"id": 132365, "content": "没看几本书 也没看几部电影 没舍得买几件称心的衣服 没收到心仪工作的面试通知 凑活的大四", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819514}, {"id": 132621, "content": "凑合着跟男朋友过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757857}, {"id": 132367, "content": "办了张健身年卡 半年过去了 体重还是这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827479}, {"id": 132623, "content": "对每个明天都是迷茫的状态，对已过的昨天是无视，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829129}, {"id": 132369, "content": "yy", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259406}, {"id": 132370, "content": "想换女朋友，但是发现其实也没什么人能比她好，就凑活过吧", "image": "img/option/option/201611101513149gcUOTZqJwkdSK7H.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429393}, {"id": 132626, "content": "不断的下决心，不断的三分钟热度。自己都瞧不起自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829008}, {"id": 132373, "content": "还没有辞职，凑合着上班，凑合着挣钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540120}, {"id": 133142, "content": "比上一年还要凑合", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831014}, {"id": 132375, "content": "生活凑合，衣服凑合，吃的也凑合，没有什么是不凑合的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757260}, {"id": 132376, "content": "双十一，各种骗你钱的商家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827084}, {"id": 134424, "content": "造化弄人只能将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802079}, {"id": 132377, "content": "凑合着生活，又酬凑合着学习 ，又酬和着思考 好失败", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803347}, {"id": 134425, "content": "造化弄人只能将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802079}, {"id": 132378, "content": "一个人挺好…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 286326}, {"id": 132379, "content": "本来想让婆媳“凑合”过过的，不想还是“爆棚”了，现在也就自己只能“凑合”着过了一年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828175}, {"id": 137499, "content": "写个稿子东拼西凑 从来没正儿八经看完一本书 硬盘里的资料乱七八糟也没下决心分类整理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829168}, {"id": 132380, "content": "从不凑合", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673407}, {"id": 132381, "content": "给女朋友一条mikimito,高兴，吃土。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707005}, {"id": 132382, "content": "本来想把懒癌治好的，但是发现是……唉！那么多字懒得打了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828194}]}